</div>
        <div><a name="sec_7.30" id="sec_7.30"></a><h2>7.30<span style="mso-tab-count:1">&#xA0; </span>domestic carriage requirement</h2>

<div align="center" class="table_container"><table class="MsoISOTable" style="mso-table-anchor-horizontal:column;mso-table-overlap:never;border-spacing:0;border-width:1px;"><a name="_22fd7556-96c5-7649-a75c-b8cc6339bc4f" id="_22fd7556-96c5-7649-a75c-b8cc6339bc4f"></a><tbody><tr><td valign="top" align="left" style="border-top:solid windowtext 1.5pt;mso-border-top-alt:solid windowtext 1.5pt;border-bottom:solid windowtext 1.5pt;mso-border-bottom-alt:solid windowtext 1.5pt;page-break-after:auto;"><p style="text-align: left;page-break-after:auto" class="MsoNormal"><a name="_68679122-d776-db8d-dcfd-0b59e6b0147b" id="_68679122-d776-db8d-dcfd-0b59e6b0147b"></a><u>IHO Definition:</u> A carriage requirement that is specific to a country or region and is based on domestic legislation or regulation.</p>

<p style="text-align: left;page-break-after:auto" class="MsoNormal"><a name="_3eae232c-a012-f817-282c-722a86fd562b" id="_3eae232c-a012-f817-282c-722a86fd562b"></a><u>Remarks:</u></p>

