</div>

<p style="text-align: left;page-break-after:auto" class="MsoNormal"><a name="_07dd9e2c-b9e1-bdf8-12a5-2fa0f8826f8e" id="_07dd9e2c-b9e1-bdf8-12a5-2fa0f8826f8e"></a><u>Remarks:</u></p>

<div class="ul_wrap" style="page-break-after:auto"><p style="mso-list:l3 level1 lfo123;page-break-after:auto" class="MsoListParagraphCxSpFirst"><a name="_0dcff6ce-26fe-f57b-698b-0da3abe9a84f" id="_0dcff6ce-26fe-f57b-698b-0da3abe9a84f"></a>No remarks.
</p>
</div>
</td></tr></tbody></table></div>
</div>
        <div><a name="sec_8.16" id="sec_8.16"></a><h2>8.16<span style="mso-tab-count:1">&#xA0; </span>support file</h2>

<div align="center" class="table_container"><table class="MsoISOTable" style="mso-table-anchor-horizontal:column;mso-table-overlap:never;border-spacing:0;border-width:1px;"><a name="_28497a6b-28da-843b-6309-758e5faf3c98" id="_28497a6b-28da-843b-6309-758e5faf3c98"></a><tbody><tr><td valign="top" align="left" style="border-top:solid windowtext 1.5pt;mso-border-top-alt:solid windowtext 1.5pt;border-bottom:solid windowtext 1.5pt;mso-border-bottom-alt:solid windowtext 1.5pt;page-break-after:auto;"><p style="text-align: left;page-break-after:auto" class="MsoNormal"><a name="_dcf73a0a-4296-8b7e-9a6f-4e65fb87e513" id="_dcf73a0a-4296-8b7e-9a6f-4e65fb87e513"></a><u>IHO Definition:</u> Information on additional files used in addition to nautical products.</p>

<div class="figdl" style="page-break-after:auto"><a><a name="_6be55bb5-0da8-ad0c-3255-3a77463c2672" id="_6be55bb5-0da8-ad0c-3255-3a77463c2672"></a></a><p style="text-indent: -2.0cm; margin-left: 2.0cm; tab-stops: 2.0cm;page-break-after:auto" class="MsoNormal"><u>Sub-attributes:</u><span style="mso-tab-count:1">&#xA0; </span><a><a name="_d234c26a-4fbe-50a9-b750-62de5df58adc" id="_d234c26a-4fbe-50a9-b750-62de5df58adc"></a></a><b>comment</b> (see <a href="#sec_7.15">Clause 7.15</a>)<br/> <b>digital signature reference</b> (see <a href="#sec_7.26">Clause 7.26</a>)<br/> <b>digital signature value</b> (see <a href="#sec_7.27">Clause 7.27</a>)<br/> <b>edition number</b> (see <a href="#sec_7.32">Clause 7.32</a>)<br/> <b>file locator</b> (see <a href="#sec_7.34">Clause 7.34</a>)<br/> <b>file name</b> (see <a href="#sec_7.35">Clause 7.35</a>)<br/> <b>issue date</b> (see <a href="#sec_7.44">Clause 7.44</a>)<br/> <b>other data type description</b> (see <a href="#sec_7.58">Clause 7.58</a>)<br/> <b>support file format</b> (see <a href="#sec_7.81">Clause 7.81</a>)<br/> <b>support file purpose</b> (see <a href="#sec_7.82">Clause 7.82</a>)<br/> <b>default locale</b> (see <a href="#sec_8.3">Clause 8.3</a>)<br/> <b>support file specification</b> (see <a href="#sec_8.17">Clause 8.17</a>)</p>
</div>

<p style="text-align: left;page-break-after:auto" class="MsoNormal"><a name="_a9d38b85-0b64-6c97-febc-582a92826d89" id="_a9d38b85-0b64-6c97-febc-582a92826d89"></a><u>Remarks:</u></p>

<div class="ul_wrap" style="page-break-after:auto"><p style="mso-list:l3 level1 lfo124;page-break-after:auto" class="MsoListParagraphCxSpFirst"><a name="_61280b0a-40c6-199d-6d71-0e152a9c8719" id="_61280b0a-40c6-199d-6d71-0e152a9c8719"></a>No remarks.
</p>
</div>
</td></tr></tbody></table></div>
</div>
        <div><a name="sec_8.17" id="sec_8.17"></a><h2>8.17<span style="mso-tab-count:1">&#xA0; </span>support file specification</h2>

<div align="center" class="table_container"><table class="MsoISOTable" style="mso-table-anchor-horizontal:column;mso-table-overlap:never;border-spacing:0;border-width:1px;"><a name="_32a32708-eae2-898b-26c0-fbe7e61cb562" id="_32a32708-eae2-898b-26c0-fbe7e61cb562"></a><tbody><tr><td valign="top" align="left" style="border-top:solid windowtext 1.5pt;mso-border-top-alt:solid windowtext 1.5pt;border-bottom:solid windowtext 1.5pt;mso-border-bottom-alt:solid windowtext 1.5pt;page-break-after:auto;"><p style="text-align: left;page-break-after:auto" class="MsoNormal"><a name="_1da8b382-c85c-ad11-9abd-66ef2ef2ad5d" id="_1da8b382-c85c-ad11-9abd-66ef2ef2ad5d"></a><u>IHO Definition:</u> The name of the product specification to which a support file adheres.</p>

<div class="figdl" style="page-break-after:auto"><a><a name="_a8054909-6793-a782-8e46-42eb6acbed5b" id="_a8054909-6793-a782-8e46-42eb6acbed5b"></a></a><p style="text-indent: -2.0cm; margin-left: 2.0cm; tab-stops: 2.0cm;page-break-after:auto" class="MsoNormal"><u>Sub-attributes:</u><span style="mso-tab-count:1">&#xA0; </span><a><a name="_0ef51626-1671-ae91-ab3a-1123bb769a2f" id="_0ef51626-1671-ae91-ab3a-1123bb769a2f"></a></a><b>edition date</b> (see <a href="#sec_7.31">Clause 7.31</a>)<br/> <b>name</b> (see <a href="#sec_7.50">Clause 7.50</a>)<br/> <b>version</b> (see <a href="#sec_7.92">Clause 7.92</a>)</p>
</div>

<p style="text-align: left;page-break-after:auto" class="MsoNormal"><a name="_3eaed8be-c1ef-3404-f320-99da17c68c2d" id="_3eaed8be-c1ef-3404-f320-99da17c68c2d"></a><u>Remarks:</u></p>

<div class="ul_wrap" style="page-break-after:auto"><p style="mso-list:l3 level1 lfo125;page-break-after:auto" class="MsoListParagraphCxSpFirst"><a name="_368db221-84af-7d21-d125-51eebbcbb203" id="_368db221-84af-7d21-d125-51eebbcbb203"></a>No remarks.
</p>
</div>
</td></tr></tbody></table></div>
</div>
        <div><a name="sec_8.18" id="sec_8.18"></a><h2>8.18<span style="mso-tab-count:1">&#xA0; </span>telecommunications</h2>

<div align="center" class="table_container"><table class="MsoISOTable" style="mso-table-anchor-horizontal:column;mso-table-overlap:never;border-spacing:0;border-width:1px;"><a name="_31fa387d-fdf3-330c-a24c-2a517c907607" id="_31fa387d-fdf3-330c-a24c-2a517c907607"></a><tbody><tr><td valign="top" align="left" style="border-top:solid windowtext 1.5pt;mso-border-top-alt:solid windowtext 1.5pt;border-bottom:solid windowtext 1.5pt;mso-border-bottom-alt:solid windowtext 1.5pt;page-break-after:auto;"><p style="text-align: left;page-break-after:auto" class="MsoNormal"><a name="_93b6c1f9-c43a-8ff7-11b3-539d67c92d02" id="_93b6c1f9-c43a-8ff7-11b3-539d67c92d02"></a><u>IHO Definition:</u> A means or channel of communicating at a distance by electrical or electromagnetic means such as telegraphy, telephony, or broadcasting.</p>

<div class="figdl" style="page-break-after:auto"><a><a name="_c9ba649d-6796-807c-a0b1-aab640ba8bbe" id="_c9ba649d-6796-807c-a0b1-aab640ba8bbe"></a></a><p style="text-indent: -2.0cm; margin-left: 2.0cm; tab-stops: 2.0cm;page-break-after:auto" class="MsoNormal"><u>Sub-attributes:</u><span style="mso-tab-count:1">&#xA0; </span><a><a name="_fe450fed-d077-e98d-a3a7-e37265af5202" id="_fe450fed-d077-e98d-a3a7-e37265af5202"></a></a><b>contact instructions</b> (see <a href="#sec_7.18">Clause 7.18</a>)<br/> <b>telecommunication identifier</b> (see <a href="#sec_7.83">Clause 7.83</a>)<br/> <b>telecommunication service</b> (see <a href="#sec_7.84">Clause 7.84</a>)</p>
</div>

<p style="text-align: left;page-break-after:auto" class="MsoNormal"><a name="_d08b81d9-c660-901e-a8ab-47fd425ffed5" id="_d08b81d9-c660-901e-a8ab-47fd425ffed5"></a><u>Remarks:</u></p>

<div class="ul_wrap" style="page-break-after:auto"><p style="mso-list:l3 level1 lfo126;page-break-after:auto" class="MsoListParagraphCxSpFirst"><a name="_bba5ee02-bee4-6b0e-2a94-37ea69db9cdf" id="_bba5ee02-bee4-6b0e-2a94-37ea69db9cdf"></a>No remarks.
</p>
</div>
</td></tr></tbody></table></div>
</div>
        <div><a name="sec_8.19" id="sec_8.19"></a><h2>8.19<span style="mso-tab-count:1">&#xA0; </span>time interval of cycle</h2>

<div align="center" class="table_container"><table class="MsoISOTable" style="mso-table-anchor-horizontal:column;mso-table-overlap:never;border-spacing:0;border-width:1px;"><a name="_64be7793-50c8-c75b-b623-442c3ebabab6" id="_64be7793-50c8-c75b-b623-442c3ebabab6"></a><tbody><tr><td valign="top" align="left" style="border-top:solid windowtext 1.5pt;mso-border-top-alt:solid windowtext 1.5pt;border-bottom:solid windowtext 1.5pt;mso-border-bottom-alt:solid windowtext 1.5pt;page-break-after:auto;"><p style="text-align: left;page-break-after:auto" class="MsoNormal"><a name="_96626643-7160-ee8f-7146-a681fd1401c5" id="_96626643-7160-ee8f-7146-a681fd1401c5"></a><u>IHO Definition:</u> The temporal interval of the cycle over which data is produced.</p>

<div class="figdl" style="page-break-after:auto"><a><a name="_d122c636-9b4f-5d7b-d974-e8092c998718" id="_d122c636-9b4f-5d7b-d974-e8092c998718"></a></a><p style="text-indent: -2.0cm; margin-left: 2.0cm; tab-stops: 2.0cm;page-break-after:auto" class="MsoNormal"><u>Sub-attributes:</u><span style="mso-tab-count:1">&#xA0; </span><a><a name="_440202ba-ccd0-8d0c-663c-740e209cfe59" id="_440202ba-ccd0-8d0c-663c-740e209cfe59"></a></a><b>type of time interval unit</b> (see <a href="#sec_7.88">Clause 7.88</a>)<br/> <b>value of time</b> (see <a href="#sec_7.91">Clause 7.91</a>)</p>
</div>

<p style="text-align: left;page-break-after:auto" class="MsoNormal"><a name="_5f41b68c-d313-2ec8-e376-edc19a029fe0" id="_5f41b68c-d313-2ec8-e376-edc19a029fe0"></a><u>Remarks:</u></p>

<div class="ul_wrap" style="page-break-after:auto"><p style="mso-list:l3 level1 lfo127;page-break-after:auto" class="MsoListParagraphCxSpFirst"><a name="_18e76d3c-2f56-bca1-91e0-aa4cfb012ec6" id="_18e76d3c-2f56-bca1-91e0-aa4cfb012ec6"></a>No remarks.
</p>
</div>
</td></tr></tbody></table></div>
</div>
        <div><a name="sec_8.20" id="sec_8.20"></a><h2>8.20<span style="mso-tab-count:1">&#xA0; </span>time interval of product</h2>

<div align="center" class="table_container"><table class="MsoISOTable" style="mso-table-anchor-horizontal:column;mso-table-overlap:never;border-spacing:0;border-width:1px;"><a name="_1082cd4b-ec3b-0dcc-8f2c-031c923fb2f8" id="_1082cd4b-ec3b-0dcc-8f2c-031c923fb2f8"></a><tbody><tr><td valign="top" align="left" style="border-top:solid windowtext 1.5pt;mso-border-top-alt:solid windowtext 1.5pt;border-bottom:solid windowtext 1.5pt;mso-border-bottom-alt:solid windowtext 1.5pt;page-break-after:auto;"><p style="text-align: left;page-break-after:auto" class="MsoNormal"><a name="_2f4af7f8-4544-e3d0-5f44-295525e7d855" id="_2f4af7f8-4544-e3d0-5f44-295525e7d855"></a><u>IHO Definition:</u> The temporal interval over which the product is updated or renewed.</p>

<div class="figdl" style="page-break-after:auto"><a><a name="_63b1b2e8-9bd3-6f1b-950d-d89841648fdf" id="_63b1b2e8-9bd3-6f1b-950d-d89841648fdf"></a></a><p style="text-indent: -2.0cm; margin-left: 2.0cm; tab-stops: 2.0cm;page-break-after:auto" class="MsoNormal"><u>Sub-attributes:</u><span style="mso-tab-count:1">&#xA0; </span><a><a name="_5f68b1c5-efa5-ae35-d82c-9d0ea31af88f" id="_5f68b1c5-efa5-ae35-d82c-9d0ea31af88f"></a></a><b>expiration date</b> (see <a href="#sec_7.33">Clause 7.33</a>)<br/> <b>issue date</b> (see <a href="#sec_7.44">Clause 7.44</a>)<br/> <b>issuance cycle</b> (see <a href="#sec_8.6">Clause 8.6</a>)</p>
</div>

<p style="text-align: left;page-break-after:auto" class="MsoNormal"><a name="_09f9563b-a816-7e13-77bb-d1f7fffa5483" id="_09f9563b-a816-7e13-77bb-d1f7fffa5483"></a><u>Remarks:</u></p>

<div class="ul_wrap" style="page-break-after:auto"><p style="mso-list:l3 level1 lfo128;page-break-after:auto" class="MsoListParagraphCxSpFirst"><a name="_0a9890a6-f72b-21d2-34c8-3119c1ee3927" id="_0a9890a6-f72b-21d2-34c8-3119c1ee3927"></a>No remarks.
</p>
</div>
</td></tr></tbody></table></div>
</div>
        <div><a name="sec_8.21" id="sec_8.21"></a><h2>8.21<span style="mso-tab-count:1">&#xA0; </span>week of year</h2>

<div align="center" class="table_container"><table class="MsoISOTable" style="mso-table-anchor-horizontal:column;mso-table-overlap:never;border-spacing:0;border-width:1px;"><a name="_40409774-3f71-b00f-0a5b-7a47a4aaeef1" id="_40409774-3f71-b00f-0a5b-7a47a4aaeef1"></a><tbody><tr><td valign="top" align="left" style="border-top:solid windowtext 1.5pt;mso-border-top-alt:solid windowtext 1.5pt;border-bottom:solid windowtext 1.5pt;mso-border-bottom-alt:solid windowtext 1.5pt;page-break-after:auto;"><p style="text-align: left;page-break-after:auto" class="MsoNormal"><a name="_be631a84-957f-7193-4fde-a68542e58198" id="_be631a84-957f-7193-4fde-a68542e58198"></a><u>IHO Definition:</u> The indication of a specific week within a specific year.</p>

<div class="figdl" style="page-break-after:auto"><a><a name="_9608766e-b811-1948-3118-9063b75dece1" id="_9608766e-b811-1948-3118-9063b75dece1"></a></a><p style="text-indent: -2.0cm; margin-left: 2.0cm; tab-stops: 2.0cm;page-break-after:auto" class="MsoNormal"><u>Sub-attributes:</u><span style="mso-tab-count:1">&#xA0; </span><a><a name="_04e1ccfe-a576-9d8d-b0e4-975f94d39815" id="_04e1ccfe-a576-9d8d-b0e4-975f94d39815"></a></a><b>week number</b> (see <a href="#sec_7.94">Clause 7.94</a>)<br/> <b>year number</b> (see <a href="#sec_7.95">Clause 7.95</a>)</p>
</div>

<p style="text-align: left;page-break-after:auto" class="MsoNormal"><a name="_57912059-235b-2c36-36d4-dd21689a8d22" id="_57912059-235b-2c36-36d4-dd21689a8d22"></a><u>Remarks:</u></p>

<div class="ul_wrap" style="page-break-after:auto"><p style="mso-list:l3 level1 lfo129;page-break-after:auto" class="MsoListParagraphCxSpFirst"><a name="_c63e3eb9-5c90-20bb-dcac-84be562c9987" id="_c63e3eb9-5c90-20bb-dcac-84be562c9987"></a>No remarks.
</p>
</div>
</td></tr></tbody></table></div>
</div>
